AdminAttendeeDetailActivity
public class AdminAttendeeDetailActivity.DownloadImageTask extends android.os.AsyncTask<String,Void,android.graphics.Bitmap>
An asynchronous task that downloads an image from a URL and sets it on an ImageView. This task ensures that image downloading does not block the main UI thread.
